    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for a daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several visible scratches, minor door dings, and some paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and signs of wear, though all electronics and the air conditioning remain fully functional. Mechanically, it runs well, though it may require some routine maintenance in the near future to keep it in peak shape. It is a solid, dependable car for someone looking for functionality over aesthetics.",
      "price": 17500.0,
