    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly fixer-upper? This vehicle is in poor condition and will need some dedicated mechanical attention and TLC to get back to its best. It\u2019s a great opportunity for someone handy looking for a diamond in the rough at a very accessible price!",
